pddl.prompt:
Your name is hanoi_planner. You are solving the Tower of Hanoi puzzle with 4 disks. You are in an environment with the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
You have the following knowledge:
{agents->hanoi_planner->private_information}
This is the goal to achieve:
{agents->hanoi_planner->goal}
Think step by step and provide the necessary PDDL domain and problem files to solve this 4-disk puzzle optimally.
Enclose the pddl domain between <domain></domain> tags, and the pddl problem between <problem></problem> tags.
